<h3>Start of the track</h3>
You can access the start of the track from Onepoto or Hopuruahine Landing via the scenic Te Urewera Rainforest Route (State Highway 38):
This driving route has long sections of unsealed gravel road and winds its way through native rainforest and past small rural settlements. 
There is parking at the Waikaremoana Holiday Park and the nearby DOC Visitor Centre, which has information on transport to the track, including water taxis and shuttles.
